The game Solitario is played by two players on a noshape board with nobasis tiling. All players play with Markers. Rules for Pieces: Markers step adjacent. Players take turns moving. Rules: Add one of your pieces to the set of empty vertexs. Aim: If a player places 3 of their pieces in an adjacent direction line, the moving player wins. The Solitario (Ludii 1) ruleset.
